{"tid":852121,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)危機解密 時凶感應 隔世救未來","createTime":"2018-10-07T15:24:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T21:15:12.000Z","uid":29160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9534bc3d74e362bab3e083b8247bf5cee99d92d","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T15:24:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEysPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=93c4c984\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEysPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=05fb841d\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEysPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=68c09f80\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/e/e5/Source_Code_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fe%2Fe5%2FSource_Code_Poster.jpg&h=80ce6935&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/cf/DejaVuBigPoster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fcf%2FDejaVuBigPoster.jpg&h=4cc561db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7f/Frequency_film.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7f%2FFrequency_film.jpg&h=cc289463&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.寇特&middot;史蒂文斯上尉（傑克&middot;葛倫霍飾）本是美國陸軍UH-60黑鷹直昇機駕駛員，某一日他發現自己變成了一個高中歷史教師蕭恩，與蕭恩曖昧中的女伴克莉絲汀娜&middot;華倫（蜜雪兒&middot;摩納漢飾）一同搭火車前往芝加哥，正當他感到丈八金剛摸不著頭緒的時候，火車爆炸了，他又回到一個軍事基地，接受柯琳&middot;古德溫上尉（薇拉&middot;法蜜嘉飾）的模擬測試，寇特被告知，他被五角大廈選中，進入了羅利奇博士（傑佛瑞&middot;懷特飾）發明的「原始碼系統」調查過去發生過的恐怖攻擊案件<br />\n<br />\n2.一眾美國海軍及家屬參加海上嘉年華，在渡輪出發後不久，船上的汽車炸彈於2006年二月十九日，懺悔星期二早上十時五十分發生爆炸，造成五百四十三人死亡。<br />\n美國菸酒槍炮及爆裂物管理局（ATF）人員道格（丹佐&middot;華盛頓飾）接手調查案件，在找尋案件證據後，證實這為一宗恐怖襲擊案，在翻查現場附近行車天橋的錄像片段後，發現事發時間有一騎機車的人正在橋中心停下觀望。其後調查人員於現場發現一具女屍<br />\n<br />\n3.1969年的10月12日，約翰的父親在布朗區的救災裏死去，而那場悲劇使得他的生活與成長過程中，皆蒙上一層無法擺脫的陰影。然而，事情經過三十年後，某天夜晚約翰意外地找到他父親生前所用的無線電，並在隨興的使用撥接之下，突然跟一位陌生男子搭上線。而且，無線電在沒有插電源的情況下，卻能依舊正常通話，更讓約翰意想不到的是，與他隔空對話的不是別人，正是他三十年前還在人世的父親<br />\n<br />\n12 00AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEysPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=76158488\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=NWnpFoJ0xcHaGSY0bhWEysPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c02cfe35\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259ee6e54015ee294990fe27b0314a66643d0ad8","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T15:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bae77860e32568c399be2019e4f54c3bc6c5c0f","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T16:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb393f8964a352ee037bd49d3995e4bedddfe0c7","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T17:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e277dd157db8fe6974259d1f2d0190f921e6f530","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T19:18:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2381916151e08e9d110fe5f453fc4dd5af9671fc","tid":852121,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T21:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}